<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Free 21-Day Dunk Plan — Good Drills</title>
<meta name="description" content="The free 21-day plan that thousands have used to add inches on their vert and start dunking. Day-by-day structure. Just follow it.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Anton&family=Archivo+Black&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --black: #000000;
    --ink: #0e0e0e;
    --paper: #ffffff;
    --paper-warm: #f5f3ee;
    --rule: #1a1a1a;
    --neon: #d6ff2e;
    --neon-deep: #b8e018;
    --neon-soft: #f9ffd6;
    --muted: #6b6b6b;
    --prep: #00b3ff;
    --prep-soft: #e3f6ff;
    --challenge: #ff3d6e;
    --challenge-soft: #ffe6ec;
    --work: #d6ff2e;
    --work-ink: #1a1a1a;
    --work-soft: #f9ffd6;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 17px;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }

  .top-banner {
    background: var(--neon);
    color: var(--black);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .masthead {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 18px 0;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--neon);
  }
  .masthead-inner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .brand {
    font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--paper);
  }
  .brand span { color: var(--neon); }
  .masthead-meta {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .hero {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 80px 0 100px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -100px;
    right: -100px;
    width: 700px;
    height: 700px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(214,255,46,0.10) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .kicker {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--neon);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: rgba(214,255,46,0.10);
    padding: 9px 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(214,255,46,0.45);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .kicker .dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--neon);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--neon);
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.35; } }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(56px, 9.5vw, 128px);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: 0.005em;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  h1 .neon-word { color: var(--neon); }

  .deck {
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 760px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .deck strong { color: var(--paper); font-weight: 700; }

  .deck-free {
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--black);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--neon);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .deck-free::before {
    content: '↓';
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .section-num {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .section-num::before {
    content: '';
    width: 28px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--neon);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(44px, 6.5vw, 80px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: 0.005em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    max-width: 880px;
  }
  .section-title .neon-word {
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--neon);
    padding: 0 10px;
  }

  .why {
    padding: 100px 0 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--paper);
  }
  .why-header { margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .why-body { max-width: 820px; }
  .why-body p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .why-body p strong { font-weight: 700; }
  .why-body p:first-of-type::first-letter {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    font-size: 84px;
    font-weight: 400;
    float: left;
    line-height: 0.85;
    margin: 8px 16px 0 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--neon);
    padding: 4px 8px 0;
  }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.78em;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    padding: 2px 9px 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    vertical-align: 2px;
    margin: 0 2px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    border-radius: 2px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .tag-prep { background: var(--prep); color: var(--paper); }
  .tag-challenge { background: var(--challenge); color: var(--paper); }
  .tag-work { background: var(--work); color: var(--work-ink); }

  .reasons { margin-top: 48px; }
  .reason {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 92px 1fr;
    gap: 28px;
    padding: 32px 0;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--ink);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .reason:last-child { border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink); }
  .reason-num {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    line-height: 0.85;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .reason-num::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 36px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--neon);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .reason-body {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    padding-top: 6px;
  }
  .reason-body strong { font-weight: 700; }
  .reason-body em.think {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-style: normal;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .reason-body em.think::before {
    content: 'THINK → ';
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }

  .why-outro {
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding: 32px;
    background: var(--paper-warm);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--neon);
  }
  .why-outro p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .why-outro p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .why-outro p strong { font-weight: 700; }

  .mid-cta {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 70px 0;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--neon);
    border-bottom: 4px solid var(--neon);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .mid-cta::before {
    content: 'DUNK EVERYTHING';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(120px, 22vw, 280px);
    color: rgba(214,255,46,0.04);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .mid-cta-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .mid-cta-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--neon);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .mid-cta-headline {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);
    line-height: 0.98;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .mid-cta-headline .neon-word { color: var(--neon); }
  .mid-cta-deck {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .mid-cta-list { list-style: none; }
  .mid-cta-list li {
    padding: 9px 0 9px 32px;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }
  .mid-cta-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .mid-cta-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 16px;
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    background: var(--neon);
    clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 100% 50%, 50% 100%, 0% 50%);
  }
  .mid-cta-list li strong { color: var(--paper); font-weight: 700; }

  .mid-cta-card {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 34px 28px 28px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 0 var(--neon);
  }
  .mid-cta-card .price-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .mid-cta-card .price-strike {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: line-through;
    font-size: 18px;
  }
  .mid-cta-card .price-now {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 64px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .mid-cta-card .price-tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: block;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--neon);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    padding: 20px 22px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border: 3px solid var(--ink);
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
    text-align: center;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--neon);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .mid-cta-card .guarantee {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-top: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .program {
    padding: 100px 0 60px;
    background: var(--paper);
  }
  .program-header { margin-bottom: 56px; }

  .key {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    background: var(--paper-warm);
    border: 2px solid var(--ink);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .key-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-right: 6px;
  }

  .days {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--ink);
  }

  .day {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    padding: 24px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    align-items: center;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }
  .day:hover { background: var(--paper-warm); }

  .day-num {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    line-height: 0.85;
  }
  .day-num .label {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .day-num .number {
    font-size: 56px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .day-num .of {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-left: 4px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .day-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px 14px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .day-headline {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 20px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .day-block {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    padding: 7px 13px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    border: 1.5px solid;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .day-block .dur {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    opacity: 0.75;
  }
  .day-block.prep { background: var(--prep-soft); border-color: var(--prep); color: var(--prep); }
  .day-block.challenge { background: var(--challenge-soft); border-color: var(--challenge); color: var(--challenge); }
  .day-block.work { background: var(--work-soft); border-color: var(--work-ink); color: var(--work-ink); }
  .day-block.work .dur { opacity: 0.6; }

  .day.off-day {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.025);
  }
  .day.off-day .day-num .number { color: var(--muted); }
  .day.off-day .day-headline {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .day.test-day {
    background: var(--neon-soft);
    border-bottom-color: var(--neon-deep);
  }
  .test-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--neon);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 5px 10px 6px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .final-cta {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 110px 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--neon);
  }
  .final-cta::before {
    content: 'DUNK';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(220px, 38vw, 540px);
    color: rgba(214,255,46,0.05);
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .final-cta-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .final-cta-kicker {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: var(--neon);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .final-cta-kicker::before, .final-cta-kicker::after {
    content: '';
    width: 44px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--neon);
  }
  .final-cta-headline {
    font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 104px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .final-cta-headline .neon-word { color: var(--neon); }
  .final-cta-deck {
    font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 20px);
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
  }

  .btn-massive {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--neon);
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Archivo Black', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    padding: 24px 52px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border: none;
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--paper);
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .btn-massive:hover {
    transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
    box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--paper);
  }
  .btn-massive:active {
    transform: translate(4px, 4px);
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--paper);
  }

  .final-cta-price {
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .final-cta-price strong {
    color: var(--neon);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .foot {
    padding: 36px 0;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }
  .foot a { color: var(--neon); text-decoration: none; }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .container { padding: 0 20px; }
    .hero { padding: 56px 0 70px; }
    .why { padding: 64px 0 56px; }
    .program { padding: 64px 0 40px; }
    .mid-cta-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .mid-cta-card { box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--neon); }
    .reason { grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr; gap: 18px; padding: 24px 0; }
    .reason-num { font-size: 52px; }
    .day { grid-template-columns: 70px 1fr; gap: 16px; padding: 18px 0; }
    .day-num .number { font-size: 38px; }
    .day-headline { font-size: 17px; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .day-block { font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 10px; }
    .final-cta { padding: 70px 0; }
    .btn-massive { font-size: 17px; padding: 20px 36px; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    * { animation: none !important; transition: none !important; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="top-banner">FREE 21-DAY PLAN · NO OPT-IN · JUST FOLLOW IT</div>

<header class="masthead">
  <div class="container masthead-inner">
    <div class="brand">GOOD <span>DRILLS</span></div>
    <div class="masthead-meta">The Free 21-Day Dunk Plan</div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="kicker"><span class="dot"></span>The Free Plan</div>
    <h1>Add <span class="neon-word">3 inches</span> on your vert in <span class="neon-word">3 weeks.</span></h1>
    <p class="deck">The 21-day plan that <strong>thousands of hoopers</strong> have used to add inches on their vert and start dunking. The full structure is below — sets, sessions, rest days. <strong>It's free. Just follow it.</strong></p>
    <div class="deck-free">Scroll to start</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-header">
      <div class="section-num">01 / The Method</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Why it <span class="neon-word">works.</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="why-body">
      <p>When anyone asks me for vertical jump advice, I ask them one thing: <strong>"Did you do Dunk Everything?"</strong> It doesn't matter if it's my siblings, a close relative, hoopers I work with, or a random person on the street. I didn't spend years cultivating the perfect 21-day jump and dunk plan for it not to be used by everyone on the planet.</p>

      <p>The training is separated into three sections — <span class="tag tag-prep">Dunk Prep</span>, <span class="tag tag-challenge">Dunk Challenge</span>, and <span class="tag tag-work">Dunk Work</span>. It's the best way to organize training so you maximize results. This layout has more testimonials behind it than any other program on the planet. Here's why it works:</p>

      <div class="reasons">

        <div class="reason">
          <div class="reason-num">01</div>
          <div class="reason-body">
